<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id60069be4-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58" identifier="/us/usc/t30/s541h"><num value="541h">§ 541h.</num><heading> Savings provision</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Nothing in this chapter shall be deemed to amend or repeal any provisions of chapter 12 of this title, or any right granted thereunder.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id60069be5-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58">(<ref href="/us/act/1955-08-11/ch795/s9">Aug. 11, 1955, ch. 795, § 9</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/69/681">69 Stat. 681</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
